air:Brand.Name: Economy Saver
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Saver
Saver
air:Brand.air:Text:
Enjoy the ability to change your flight dates and earn twice as many miles when you book an Economy Flexi Saver trip instead!
You get: 1) Ability to change flight dates 2) 2 times as many miles accrued

Our Economy Class innovative design minimizes intrusion into your personal space even as the passenger in front reclines; while ergonomic styling of the seat further maximizes knee and legroom. It also features a headrest that can be adjusted as desired for greater support.
An easily accessible seatback-mounted handset, personal and non-intrusive reading light and in-seat power supply, are just some of the many intelligent touches designed with you in mind. (Applicable to most aircraft types)
Enjoy a sweet deal on Singapore Airlines

air:Brand.air:Text:
Cathay Pacific Makes your Economy Class Experience Better than Ever
• A cradle mechanism in the seat back allows for 6 inches recline • Headrest with side wings adjusts four ways to provide maximum head and neck support • Signature Chinese dishes alongside wide range of cuisines from around the world • 9-inch touch-screen personal TV with hundreds of Audio and Video on Demand selections • On-board Power Supply for laptop or other device, and a USB port
* If the flight will be operated by another airline or due to operational requirements, the inflight product and service may be different.
Makes your Economy Class experience better than ever, beginning with your seat.
